  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a pan over medium heat and sauté the onions until caramelized.",
    "Add ginger and garlic and sauté for another minute.",
    "Add pork steaks and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add chana dal, cumin powder, turmeric powder, garam masala powder, and salt. Cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add 200ml of water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 15 minutes.",
    "Let the mixture cool slightly.",
    "Add lemon juice and mix well.",
    "Using your hands, shape the mixture into small vadas.",
    "Heat oil in a pan over medium-high heat and fry the vadas until crispy and golden brown.",
    "Serve hot with a dollop of raita, if desired."
